FAQ_TITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Frequently Asked Questions About Making Wants
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about using our app to make your wants a reality
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What is the app for making wants?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app is designed to help you clearly define and track your wants or desires in life. By articulating your wants, you take the first step towards making them a reality.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Simply open the app and start listing out all your wants - big or small. You can categorize them, set reminders, and track your progress towards achieving each want.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What are the benefits of using this app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Having your wants written down makes them feel more tangible. The app helps you prioritize and focus on what you really want in life. It also allows you to celebrate small wins along the way.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is the app free to use?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, the basic version of the app is completely free to download and use. We offer an optional premium upgrade with advanced features like cloud syncing and analytics.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How can I get started with the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Just download the app from your device's app store and create an account. The intuitive interface will guide you through listing out all your wants and desires.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Goal Achiever
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does Goal Achiever help me reach my goals?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Goal Achiever is designed to break down your big goals into manageable steps. It provides tools to track your progress, set reminders, and celebrate milestones along the way.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can I use Goal Achiever for any kind of goal?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, Goal Achiever can be used for personal, professional, or passion goals across any area of life - fitness, finance, career, education, hobbies, and more.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How do I get started with Goal Achiever?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Sign up for a free account, then input your overarching goal. Goal Achiever will guide you through breaking it down into action steps with deadlines.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is there a desktop version or is it mobile only?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Goal Achiever has both a mobile app and desktop web application so you can access and update your goals anytime, anywhere.
